Apple iPhone 11 Pro and 11 Pro Max won the ‘Best Smartphone Camera’ award in Smartphone Awards 2019 which is annually hosted by tech youtuber Marques Brownlee @mkbhd

Google Pixel 4 is the runner up of this category.

Watch the full Smartphone Awards 2019 on @mkbhd’s YouTube channel.
